it.polimi.deib.newdem.adrenaline.model.game.turn

Class RoundRobin<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.deib.newdem.adrenaline.model.game.turn.RoundRobin<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the element cotained in this RoundRobin

    public class RoundRobin<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds a queue of elements to be executed in order. An element may add zero or more new element to this RoundRobin during its execution. This class is used by GameImpl to store a queue of Turns.
    See Also:
    GameImpl, Turn
